1
00:00:00,087 --> 00:00:02,562
Scene 3 covers function expressions

2
00:00:02,950 --> 00:00:04,450
Unlike declarations

3
00:00:04,825 --> 00:00:08,900
function expressions can be defined as part of a larger expression

4
00:00:09,287 --> 00:00:10,400
They are not hoisted

5
00:00:10,925 --> 00:00:13,350
meaning they cannot be called before being defined

